OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1777025179
OL,3,CJersey may face assisted dying
OL,4,Cstumbling block, warns pro-choice
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FA pro-choice campaign group in the UK
OL,8,Fhas warned Jersey's assisted dying
OL,9,Fbill could face a similar fate to the
OL,10,FIsle of Man.
OL,12,FThe fellow Crown Dependency passed its
OL,13,Fown law in 2025, but the UK's Ministry
OL,14,Fof Justice asked the Manx government
OL,15,Fto review it again and include more
OL,16,Fsafeguards to strengthen it before it
OL,17,Freceives Royal Assent.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
