PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1777025179
OL,3,CJersey may face assisted dying
OL,4,Cstumbling block, warns pro-choice
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FCrown Dependencies like the Isle of
OL,8,FMan and Jersey require Royal Assent to
OL,9,Fbecome legal, which is where the
OL,10,Fmonarch agrees to make a Bill into an
OL,11,FAct of Parliament.
OL,13,FNathan Stilwell from the pro-assisted
OL,14,Fdying group, Humanists UK, told ITV
OL,15,FNews: "We think it's questionable why
OL,16,Fthe UK has blocked the Isle of Man's
OL,17,Flaw.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1777025179
OL,3,CJersey may face assisted dying
OL,4,Cstumbling block, warns pro-choice
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F"There are nine European countries
OL,8,Fthat have working assisted dying laws
OL,9,Fin some form, and they've all been
OL,10,Fseen to be compliant with the European
OL,11,FCourt of Human Rights."
OL,13,FJersey's Attorney General, Matthew
OL,14,FJowitt KC, previously warned the UK
OL,15,Fthat the island could face a
OL,16,F"constitutional crisis" if it became
OL,17,Finvolved in Jersey's bill.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1777025179
OL,3,CJersey may face assisted dying
OL,4,Cstumbling block, warns pro-choice
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FMr Jowitt said: "I would be astonished
OL,8,Fif it did not receive Royal Assent; if
OL,9,Fit didn't, we would be facing a
OL,10,Fconstitutional difficulty of some
OL,11,Fmagnitude."
OL,13,FIn February, after years of debate,
OL,14,Fscrutiny and consultations, Jersey's
OL,15,FStates Members approved the landmark
OL,16,Flegislation by 32 votes to 16.
OL,18,FHow does the Isle of Man bill differ
OL,19,Ffrom Jersey?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1777025179
OL,3,CJersey may face assisted dying
OL,4,Cstumbling block, warns pro-choice
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FThe Isle of Man became the first place
OL,8,Fin the British Isles to pass its own
OL,9,FAssisted Dying Bill in March 2025.
OL,11,FYet there are differences between the
OL,12,Ftwo bills. Jersey has different
OL,13,Fresidency requirements, meaning
OL,14,Fsomeone could live on the island for a
OL,15,Fshorter amount of time before being
OL,16,Feligible for an assisted death, if
OL,17,Fthey meet the rest of the criteria.
OL,19,FJersey's bill also went through a
OL,20,Fdifferent route, with extensive
OL,21,Fscrutiny and consultation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1777025179
OL,3,CJersey may face assisted dying
OL,4,Cstumbling block, warns pro-choice
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FMr Stilwell said: "We would hope that
OL,8,Fthis would satisfy the UK Government
OL,9,Fthat the assisted dying law is going
OL,10,Fto be safe, workable and
OL,11,Fcompassionate."
OL,13,FDepending on how long the Royal Assent
OL,14,Fprocess takes, the first assisted
OL,15,Fdeath in Jersey could be as soon as
OL,16,Fnext summer, according to Jersey's
OL,17,FHealth Minister, Deputy Tom Binet -
OL,18,Fwho says it is a "world-class assisted
OL,19,Fdying law".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1777025179
OL,3,CJersey may face assisted dying
OL,4,Cstumbling block, warns pro-choice
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FThe law will go further than similar
OL,8,Flegislation that is being discussed
OL,9,Facross the UK, as eligible terminally
OL,10,Fill Jersey residents will be able to
OL,11,Fhave their life ended by a willing
OL,12,Fhealthcare professional.
OL,14,FIn a statement, Humanists UK said:
OL,15,F"Jersey's compassionate assisted dying
OL,16,Flaw has undergone years of thorough
OL,17,Fscrutiny, and we consider it to be
OL,18,Ffully compliant with the European
OL,19,FConvention on Human Rights.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1777025179
OL,3,CJersey may face assisted dying
OL,4,Cstumbling block, warns pro-choice
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F"Following the UK Government's
OL,8,Fdecision to prevent the Isle of Man's
OL,9,Flaw from proceeding at this stage, it
OL,10,Fwould be egregious for it to use the
OL,11,Fsame argument to delay or obstruct
OL,12,FJersey's progress, to the detriment of
OL,13,Fterminally ill people and their
OL,14,Ffamilies, who had hoped this law would
OL,15,Fprovide greater choice and dignity at
OL,16,Fthe end of life.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1777025179
OL,3,CJersey may face assisted dying
OL,4,Cstumbling block, warns pro-choice
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F"Given that similar laws are already
OL,8,Fin place elsewhere in Europe, it is
OL,9,Fentirely reasonable to question
OL,10,Fwhether reliance on the ECHR is
OL,11,Fjustified. Switzerland's law is one
OL,12,Fline long and has never been
OL,13,Fsuccessfully challenged under the
OL,14,FECHR."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
